<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Verify Your Email Address</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; color: #333;">
  <div style="margin: auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
    <h2 style="color: #333;">Hello!</h2>

    <p>Thank you for registering an account at <strong>{{website}}</strong>.</p>

    <p>Please click the link below to verify your email address:</p>

    <p>
      <a href="{{verifyUrl}}" style="color: #007bff; word-break: break-word;" target="_blank">
        {{verifyUrl}}
      </a>
    </p>

    <p>If you did not request this email verification, you can safely ignore this message.</p>

    <p style="margin-top: 40px;">Best regards,<br/>The <strong>{{website}}</strong> Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
